(1)
East 3rd Street, at, adjoining and west of the S.W. corner of Tompkins Street. Note demolition of Nos. 424-418 inclusive, for the widening of Tompkins Street; a link of the new East River Drive.

March 17, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
A view further westward from No. 414; a garage. Note demolition of buildings at Nos. 404-06.

March 24, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
